map m feedkeys <Left>
map n feedkeys <Down>
map e feedkeys <Up>
map i feedkeys <Right>

map <S-j> feedkeys N
map <S-k> feedkeys E
map [normal] N feedkeys <PageDown>
map [normal] E feedkeys <PageUp>
map [normal] <C-n> feedkeys <PageDown> # shift mappings are broken for whatever reason so i decided to switch to control (im using an hhkb)
map [normal] <C-e> feedkeys <PageUp>

map h feedkeys m
map j feedkeys n
map k feedkeys e
map l feedkeys i

